{"tid":359161,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"樂基兒孖未婚夫玩轉海陸空","createTime":"2017-08-14T09:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T09:37:17.000Z","uid":731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb8f359ec5e6d0e615bb9847461b9318c7f22c83","tid":359161,"uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:26:12.000Z","msg":"36歲樂基兒與黎明離婚5年，早前宣布於本月27日（美國時間）與經營有機生意商人未婚夫Ian在美國結婚，出席婚禮的主要是雙方家人和她兒時的同學，沒有邀請香港的朋友。日前樂基兒與Ian已飛到美國作準備，他們四處遊玩，玩得盡情，似預支蜜月。<br />\n<br />\n樂基兒連日來在社交平台上載進行不同戶外活動的照片，如身處大峽谷、坐氫氣球、騎馬、玩攀山及行吊橋，又在酒店泳池嬉水，Ian陪伴在她身旁。樂基兒仍堅持練習瑜伽，去到邊都不忘練習一下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uUFvrP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uUFvrP&d=cqbi2kXyh4JtWBI989%2FLTL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d3bc8f78\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uUFvrP</a>"},{"pid":"b698ca251f0b554eb6286ddc00bb859237161329","tid":359161,"uid":91620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:32:45.000Z","msg":"黎生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769ab08a101868e6f1bb81ed01ac3510309aa23b","tid":359161,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"苦戀拖得太久讓我默默退後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}